{"tid":1839733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（超快速）武漢醫院物資只夠三天用","createTime":"2020-01-24T14:28:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T14:42:47.000Z","uid":240448,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eb639c5015189936c4552ff2e12c3ab04eb635fd","tid":1839733,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:28:31.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】新型冠狀病毒疫情在武漢迅速擴散，有民眾擔心封城後，醫療物資和人手短缺。較早時，央視公布<em><span style=\"color: orange;\">武漢一線醫生的信息，提到發燒病人人數眾多，擔心無法得到及時治療</span></em>。 <br />\n<br />\n日前微博流傳這條短片，一個身穿防護衣戴N95口罩的男人拿着電話，情緒激動，旁邊有女同事試圖安慰，但不得要領。上載的人同時發文說，他們的醫療物資跟不上，身心都超負荷。<br />\n<br />\n不過相關片段其後被刪除，沒法證實影片的真實性，但就引發網民熱議，擔心前線醫生抗疫期間，承受龐大壓力，亦有人擔心武漢封城後，醫療物資不足。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中央電視台日前在《新聞1+1》中，公布武漢一線醫生的信息，提到發燒病人人數眾多，無法得到及時收治，而收治的病人無法進行及時的病源檢測，<em><span style=\"color: gold;\">導致出現交叉感染，同時當局還沒有要求定點醫院的醫護人員集中住宿，一眾醫護下班後，仍能正常離開醫院回家，沒有切斷他們被外界感染的傳播渠道。</span></em><br />\n<br />\n央視又引述全國政協委員北京腦血管病中心主任凌鋒指，武漢醫院<em><span style=\"color: gold;\">防護備嚴重不足，建議試劑盡快發放到基層。</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">為抗疫情，多個省巿包括上海、無錫及四川等，組織醫療隊前往湖北，協助新型冠狀病毒肺炎的救治工作。</span></span></em>"},{"pid":"bf17394226cda0df7e338c5348584d04e5b2d454","tid":1839733,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:30:02.000Z","msg":"消息指有武漢醫院物資只夠三天用<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=378023&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378023%26refer%3DShare&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77TYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=6766074e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378023%26refer%3DShare&h=c1132fec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=378023&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"6f0de44540078cdcf32fdcfdf2058b03f78f4740","tid":1839733,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:31:38.000Z","msg":"底死"},{"pid":"fd90035975eba8bec3e6b27f662799e2d27b9884","tid":1839733,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:35:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"358c50df0442e79866e99c0b548b955b55db651d","tid":1839733,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d9e039dd63ffd042eabce3bfbc20ed95ee574409","tid":1839733,"uid":82090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:39:47.000Z","msg":"世界第一大國喎<br />\n一個肺炎起你全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484346db5dbcaab2f2662607006661f90d3469d1","tid":1839733,"uid":217383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:41:25.000Z","msg":"之後就湧黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fafe4aba614ad066cc31f28d68d4aec807d2137","tid":1839733,"uid":300006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:42:47.000Z","msg":"繼續相信黨"}]}